data.description: Welcome home!   This beautiful and well maintained home is nestled in a small quiet subdivision less than 2 miles to I-84.  Some of the amazing features - a huge kitchen with granite, backsplash, recessed lights, stainless steel appliances, and hardwood flooring.  Additional amenities include the large great with a gas fireplace to provide ambiance and additional heat.  The large master bedroom feels very open with 10' ceilings, separate shower, an over sized soaker tub and RV parking. You will love to entertain guests in the backyard under the covered patio, or surrounding the fire pit.
